            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Up to 5 products per single image or video post, and up to 20 products per carousel post. In Stories, one product sticker per frame. In Reels, product tags appear as a shopping bag icon in the corner of the video. In Live, you can pin one featured product at a time.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
